data.description: Welcome to historic Carthage! This beautiful home has a lot of the original details, wood floors, light fixtures and basement. Sellers have put in energy efficient HVAC system, double hung/insulated glass windows, updated breaker panel/weather head, and water heater! Formal dining room, large family room and updated kitchen. There is a 1 car detached garage with generously sized fenced-in backyard with alley access. You'll want to see the charm of this classic home in person!
